    "description": "Interfactory, Inc. engages in the cloud commerce platform business in Japan. It operates through Cloud Commerce Platform, E-commerce business growth support project, and Data Utilization Platform Business segments. The company offers EBISUMART a cloud commerce platform system that allows users to build an e-commerce (EC) site; EBISUMART BtoB, a cloud commerce platform that systemizes order processing in business-to-business transactions; EBISUMART Lite, a cloud commerce platform that allows users to build EC sites for small starts; EBISUMART Enterprise, a commerce platform for large-scale EC sites; and EBISU GROWTH, a service that provides support for the growth of EC business. It also provides EBISU PIM, a product data integration platform that integrates the wide variety of product data held by companies. The company was incorporated in 2003 and is headquartered in Chiyoda, Japan."
